\begin_inset Formula $<0.01$
\end_inset 

) for T\SpecialChar ~
Tau, according to 
\begin_inset ERT
status Collapsed

\layout Standard

\backslash 
citet{basri:1990}
\end_inset 

; hence, the observation is not corrected for veiling.
 The model consists of the magnetosphere, the bipolar wind, and the accretion
